dct_title_s: AAA France & Benelux countries : including Belgium, Netherlands, Luxembourg / original cartography [copyright] The Automobile Association of Great Britain 1998.
dct_description_sm: Road map. Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Panel title. Copyright: AAA with distribution rights within the Americas. Printed in 2 segments: Northern France, Belgium, Netherlands & Luxembourg -- Central & southern France. Includes notes, indexes of places, 3 ancillary city route maps, ancillary Corsica map, ancillary distance/travel-time map, and color illustrations.
